
extends help

block prepend variables
  - var pageID = 'help-tags'
  - var pageHeading = 'List of Tags'

block content
  div
    p A tag is a label that classifies eprints in a non-hierarchical manner. Using the tags makes it easier to find articles with specific features.
    ul
      each entry in tags
        li
          strong= entry.tag
          | : #{entry.description}
